---
import LayoutStacked from '../app/LayoutStacked.astro';
---

<LayoutStacked>
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow mt-10 mb-20">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Terms and Conditions</h1>
		
		<div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-4">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">1. Introduction</h2>
				<p>Welcome to MBG Rescue Network. By using our service, you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">2. Use of Service</h2>
				<p>Users must provide accurate information when registering. The platform is designed to facilitate food rescue; any misuse for commercial gain or illegal activities is strictly prohibited.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">3. Responsibilities</h2>
				<p><strong>Providers (Schools):</strong> Must ensure food safety and quality at the time of posting. Descriptions and pickup times must be accurate.</p>
				<p><strong>Receivers (Volunteers):</strong> Must adhere to pickup deadlines and handle food with care. Failure to pick up reserved items repeatedly may result in account suspension.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">4. Data and Privacy</h2>
				<p>We collect minimal data necessary for coordination. By using MBG Rescue, you consent to sharing your location and organization name with relevant parties during the rescue process.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">5. Termination</h2>
				<p>We reserve the right to suspend accounts that violate safety protocols or display non-collaborative behavior.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
				<p>MBG Rescue Network is a coordination platform. We are not liable for the quality of food or any incidents occurring during the pickup process.</p>
			</section>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
			<a href="/authentication/sign-up" class="text-primary-700 hover:underline dark:text-primary-500 font-medium">
				&larr; Back to Registration
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</LayoutStacked>
